            v-list-item-title {{ perfil.name }}
      v-container( class="d-flex flex-row-reverse")
        v-btn
          v-icon mdi-shuffle
</template>
<script>
export default {

    elegit: [
      {
        name: 'Mike Carlson',

      },
      {
        name: 'Cindy Baker',
        avatar: 'https://cdn.vuetifyjs.com/images/lists/3.jpg'
      },
      {
        name: 'Ali Connors',
        avatar: 'https://cdn.vuetifyjs.com/images/lists/4.jpg'
      }
    ]
  })
}
</script>
